# Story Universe Engine

- **Fases 1–4 antes de historias:** ingest → knowledge base → taxonomía → perfiles cóctel.
- EPUBs en `corpus/epubs/` (gitignored). No persistir prosa protegida.
- Prisma: `CocktailNarrativeProfile`, `Story`, `StoryScript`, `StoryStoryboard`, `StoryAnimationPrompt`.
- CLI: `npm run ingest:literary-corpus`, `build:knowledge-base`, `build:cocktail-profiles`, `generate:stories`, …
- Docs: `docs/story-universe/01_universe_overview.md`
- Remotion episodios: `remotion/story-episode/`
- Reutilizar `lib/ai/provider.ts`, `classic-cartoon-prompts.ts`, `inferLiquidTone`.
